name: CoreAPI Security_User
description: API to access manage user information
about:
Description

The CoreAPI Security_User API enables manage user information that can be also viewed in the User tool.

With this API, you can list all existing users within the system, fetch all information regarding a specific user, delete a user and create/save a user.

Prerequisites: In order for the API to work, you will have to change the endpoint in the General tab.

Operations  performed

Important note: Please review the definitions and the request/response bodies for each operation. In certain definitions, you will a description next each field. If not, view the example data in the selected operation.

/List

Get the list of existing users. Within each object in the returned array, the UUID of each item is placed. This is the same value that /Get operation requires.

In the example data, you will find the response body of this operation.
